  "ESC_EYDESCRIPTION": "This document is the Functional Requirement Specification that describes the functionalities of the Sales & Distribution Module of SAP S/4 HANA System. An approved URS acts as an input to this document. This document shall form the basis for the software design specification document and operational qualification testing for the system so as to meet business requirements as well as compliance with applicable regulatory requirements. <br/><br/>Part of work product for upgrading from SAP application to S/4 HANA to enhance business processes and IT Infrastructure and planning other strategies for achieving organization’s growth and future vision in pharmaceutical sector.",
